07:00.826 --> 07:03.863
and he's gonna make you grow up
to be big and strong for....

07:04.205 --> 07:05.699
Grow, B.A., grow.

07:06.249 --> 07:08.241
l don't need to grow, fool.

07:09.001 --> 07:10.164
Face.

07:12.129 --> 07:13.540
Get hold of Tawnia.

07:13.631 --> 07:16.122
See what she's got
