with just about everybody.

13:42.520 --> 13:45.437
He used to run a cycle repair shop
over on Pico.

13:45.940 --> 13:47.434
He's a huge guy.

13:47.984 --> 13:51.684
Gentlemen, we're gonna see Tiny Roscoe.

13:56.200 --> 13:57.860
Who's Tiny Roscoe?

13:58.035 --> 13:59.494
[Metal clinking]

14:01.664 --> 14:03.953
