for a spin in the chariot of their dreams.

18:08.953 --> 18:11.195
Sort of helped them
make up their mind, l think.

18:11.289 --> 18:14.455
Hey, Jack. Get this flake out of here.

18:15.626 --> 18:18.829
Wait a minute. Now, tossing out
the best salesman you ever had...

18:18.921 --> 18:20.878
